name: Canada's NEWEST Charter Airline! Aeroflyer Boeing 737-600 at Calgary Airport [4K]
description:
On April 11th, KF Aerospace of Kelowna, BC, announced the launch of a new charter carrier known as Aeroflyer.

What’s really interesting though, is that they’re starting operations with two former WestJet Boeing 737-600s!

Here's a look at Aeroflyer's first arrival into Calgary!
